									</svg>
									<span class="text-gray-700">Support system evaluation</span>
								</li>
							</ul>

							<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Readiness Assessment</h4>
							<ul class="space-y-3">
								<li class="flex items-start">
